text: Kilcommon GAA or CLG Cill Chomáin as it is known in Irish is a Gaelic football club located in Kilcommon in north-western County Mayo. The club colours are white and black. ==History== Kilcommon won the Mayo County Junior championship in 2005 and 2012 beating Castlebar (B Team) and Ardnaree respectively. Kilcommon reached the Mayo Junior County Semi final in 2020 where they were beaten by Kilmaine ==Achievements== ==References== ==External links== Category:Gaelic football clubs in County Mayo Category:Gaelic Athletic Association clubs in County Mayo
